v0.19.0

# Changes

## Feature

 - Add an operator that will manage the lifecycle of the existing handler. It syncs the CRDs, the namespace (if different than the operator), the RBAC, and the handler itself. ([#466](https://github.com/nmstate/kubernetes-nmstate/pull/466), [@bcrochet](https://github.com/bcrochet))

## Other (Bug, Cleanup or Flake)

 - Adapt scc.yaml to ocp-4.5 ([#502](https://github.com/nmstate/kubernetes-nmstate/pull/502), [@qinqon](https://github.com/qinqon))

